DZD - Algerian Dinar

The Algerian Dinar is the currency of Algeria. Our currency rankings show that the most popular Algerian Dinar exchange rate is the DZD to USD rate. The currency code for Dinars is DZD , and the currency symbol is دج. Below, you'll find Algerian Dinar rates and a currency converter.
